message.content:
There are several NASA project codes, where each code refers to a specific mission or program. Some of these project codes include:

1. ISS – International Space Station
2. JWST – James Webb Space Telescope
3. SLS – Space Launch System
4. HLS - Human Landing System (Artemis)
5. MSL – Mars Science Laboratory (Curiosity Rover)
6. MER – Mars Exploration Rovers (Spirit and Opportunity Rovers)
7. MAVEN - Mars Atmosphere and Volatile Evolution mission 
8. OSIRIS-REx - Origins, Spectral Interpretation, Resource Identification, Security-Regolith Explorer asteroid sampling mission 
9 .TESS: Transiting Exoplanet Survey Satellite 

However, it is important to note that some of these projects are ongoing while others have been completed or retired from operation.
